                <head>349. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>At the 373d Meeting of the National Security Council on July 24, Secretary
                        <persName>Dulles</persName> briefed the Council on his discussions with the
                    British on Kuwait. For the memorandum of discussion of this meeting, see <ref
                        target="#d31">Document 31</ref>.</p>
